    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When the troubadour attempts to lie through truth-detecting magic, zones of truth, or other, similar effects, the caster of those effects no longer gains a caster level check (MSB check) to attempt to force the troubadour to tell the truth. When he uses the Bluff skill to pass a secret message, the words and meaning of his secret messages cannot be gleaned from him or those he directly delivers the message to by divinations unless the caster succeeds at a caster level check (MSB check) against a DC of 15 + the troubadour&#8217;s level. The troubadour must be 4th level and possess the flexible truth class feature to gain this actor training.</p>\n",
